<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SkyHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css">
</head>

<body>

  <%- include partials/header.ejs %>
  <%- include partials/navbar.ejs %>
  <br>

  <section class="hero-section">
    <video autoplay muted loop id="video-background">
      <source src="/video/Video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
      Your browser does not support the video tag.
    </video>
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Welcome to SkyHub</h1>
      <p>Your gateway to seamless and enjoyable travel experiences</p>
      <button class="cta-button">Learn More</button>
    </div>
  </section>



  <section class="featured-content">
    <h2>Featured Airlines</h2>

    <div class="airline">
      <img src="/images/Airlines/Emirates-Airlines.jpg" alt="Emirates Airlines">
      <h3>Emirates Airlines</h3>
      <p>Connecting you to the world with luxury and comfort.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="airline">
      <img src="/images/Airlines/Singapore_Airlines.jpg" alt="Singapore Airlines">
      <h3>Singapore Airlines</h3>
      <p>A symbol of excellence in air travel, offering exceptional service and hospitality.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="airline">
      <img src="/images/Airlines/delta.jpg" alt="Delta Air Lines">
      <h3>Delta Air Lines</h3>
      <p>Experience the world with Delta Air Lines, known for its extensive route network, superior service, and commitment to passenger satisfaction.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="airline">
      <img src="/images/Airlines/British-Airways.webp" alt="British Airways">
      <h3>British Airways</h3>
      <p>Fly with elegance and sophistication on British Airways, offering a blend of tradition and innovation for a truly exceptional journey.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="airline">
      <img src="/images/Airlines/lufthansa.jpg" alt="Lufthansa">
      <h3>Lufthansa</h3>
      <p>Experience German precision and hospitality with Lufthansa, connecting you to a vast network of destinations with top-notch service.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="airline">
      <img src="/images/Airlines/Qatar-airways.jpg" alt="Qatar Airways">
      <h3>Qatar Airways</h3>
      <p>Experience world-class service and hospitality with Qatar Airways, connecting you to over 160 destinations worldwide.</p>
    </div>

  </section>



  <section class="deals-and-promotions">
    <h2>Deals and Promotions</h2>

    <div class="deal">
      <img src="/images/Deals/hotel.webp" alt="Beach Getaway Deal">
      <h3>Beach Getaway Deal</h3>
      <p>Escape to a tropical paradise with our Beach Getaway Deal. Enjoy discounted fares to stunning beach destinations. Hurry, limited time offer!</p>
      <p><strong>Valid until: August 31, 2024</strong></p>
      <a href="#" style="color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none; display: block; margin-top: 10px;">Learn More</a>
    </div>

    <div class="deal">
      <img src="/images/Deals/mountain.jpg" alt="Mountain Adventure Deal">
      <h3>Mountain Adventure Deal</h3>
      <p>Embark on a thrilling adventure with our Mountain Adventure Deal. Save on flights to breathtaking mountain landscapes. Book now for an adrenaline-packed journey!</p>
      <p><strong>Valid until: September 15, 2024</strong></p>
      <a href="#" style="color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none; display: block; margin-top: 10px;">Learn More</a>
    </div>


  </section>


  <section class="popular-destinations">
    <h2>Popular Destinations</h2>

    <div class="destination">
      <img src="/images/Destinations/Tokyo.jpg" alt="Tokyo, Japan">
      <h3>Tokyo, Japan</h3>
      <p>Experience the vibrant culture of Tokyo, Japan. Enjoy modern skyscrapers, traditional temples, and delicious cuisine.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="destination">
      <img src="/images/Destinations/new-york.jpg" alt="New York, USA">
      <h3>New York, USA</h3>
      <p>Discover the city that never sleeps. New York offers a mix of iconic landmarks, Broadway shows, and diverse neighborhoods.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="destination">
      <img src="/images/Destinations/sydney.jpg" alt="Sydney, Australia">
      <h3>Sydney, Australia</h3>
      <p>Experience the stunning landscapes of Sydney, Australia. Enjoy the famous Sydney Opera House, beautiful beaches, and vibrant culture.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="destination">
      <img src="/images/Destinations/Italy.jpg" alt="Rome, Italy">
      <h3>Rome, Italy</h3>
      <p>Immerse yourself in the rich history of Rome, Italy. Explore ancient ruins like the Colosseum and indulge in authentic Italian cuisine.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="destination">
      <img src="/images/Destinations/greece.webp" alt="Santorini, Greece">
      <h3>Santorini, Greece</h3>
      <p>Experience the breathtaking views of Santorini, Greece. Explore the charming white-washed buildings, crystal-clear waters, and stunning sunsets.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="destination">
      <img src="/images/Destinations/cape.jpg" alt="Cape Town, South Africa">
      <h3>Cape Town, South Africa</h3>
      <p>Discover the diverse landscapes of Cape Town, South Africa. From Table Mountain to beautiful beaches, experience the unique culture and wildlife.</p>
    </div>



  </section>



  <%- include partials/footer.ejs %>
</body>

</html>
